text: Kihikihi is a small town in the Waikato Region of the North Island. It is located on State Highway 3 and is 5 kilometers south of Te Awamutu. The town's outer rim has been swallowed up by Te Awamutu with the golf course located in between the towns. It has a primary school in the town. == References == Category:Towns in Waikato Category:Waipa District
title: Kihikihi
